{
  "texts": [
    "Software systems for automated performance monitoring and automated regression testing, which use virtual users from various geographical areas, have been in existence for around 10 to 15 years.",
    "These tools have the capacity to imitate human workers and execute repetitive duties such as regression monitoring and testing of diverse web apps and front-end desktop.",
    "According to Lubis and Sembiring [14], RPA represents a logical advancement of these capabilities.",
    "A variety of companies provide RPA products, as identified by Van Der Aalst,Bichler,and Heinzl [15].",
    "These providers include UiPath, Automation Edge, Softomotive, Automation Anywhere, Pegasystems, Blue Prism, Kryon systems, Cognizant, Kofax, Conduent."
  ]
}